Span.Text: "We did a number of trials around collaboration and email systems and found users preferred Office 365 for its functionality, and ability to work well both in the office and also on mobile devices."
David Henderson, Chief Information Office, A&N Media
A&N Media uses Microsoft Azure cloud platform and Office 365 to provide collaboration suite for round-the-clock news gathering.
Click to view full case study

Microsoft mobility solutions provide financial advisors with rapid and highly secure access to customer account data and financial histories, so they have complete customer profiles to tailor financial advice and recommendations on the go. This, coupled with Microsoft Dynamics CRM, provides a customisable, scalable platform that can easily integrate with existing line-of-business systems.

Microsoft mobility solutions, coupled with enterprise social and CRM tools, empower your staff with contextual analytics, intuitive case tracking, and internal collaboration tools to deliver high-quality service and streamlined issue resolution on the go. Innovative engaging app experiences boost customer confidence by presenting financial data in a sharable, collaborative form factor, leading to greater loyalty, referrals, and sales.

Using Microsoft’s mobility technology, financial service providers are set apart from competitors.  Customers recognise the innovation and are ready to meet face-to-face, where financial planners can spend more time listening and less time dealing with technology.

Unlock data and business logic in legacy systems, and expose that data and logic to employees through more effective and faster to deploy modern applications and devices. Windows devices offer superior functionality and a diversity of form factors, all within a highly secure mobile device that is encrypted and remotely managed while providing simple, direct-access to corporate network resources.
